Define the choices available on this choiceDef, separated by semicolons. Just like the [text](Text_%28GUI_item_property%29 "Text (GUI item property)") property, can also take string parameters in the "\#str\_nnnnn" format.

This property is restricted to the [choiceDef](ChoiceDef_%28GUI_item_type%29 "ChoiceDef (GUI item type)") item type.

Syntax
------

    choices choices

Default value
-------------

    Unknown

Example(s)
----------

    choices "No;Yes"
    choices "#str_04221"

